{"tid":1340132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗人入一入","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:12:57.000Z","uid":162927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3cfe6c783c63316cf699b5b376789534e05a57","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"第一次開post，請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係一個元朗人，今晚元朗既情況大家都見到，班鄉黑周圍打人，仲上埋元朗西鐵站，打999，一直只係回答元朗同事會處理。一個鐘之後先有警察到現場。<br />\n先唔講係咪警黑合作，光復元朗亦係後話。<br />\n聽日各位元朗人去元朗警署投訴，唔知有幾多人和應，最好做到包圍警署咁。<br />\n例子參考沙田新城市活動。<br />\n求指教。<br />\n作為一個元朗人，西鐵站差唔多係出去既主要交通工具，呢個地方竟然變得咁危險，好想做啲野。"},{"pid":"9bac3501c8955269234555e47815a87832686883","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d646f376ce9820da9b67bf5dc02b30da175c44f","tid":1340132,"uid":70650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acae0009eec459d2b0b2e2c353945114a161f50a","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:57:01.000Z","msg":"元朗人入"},{"pid":"0494c12e8aebaf1d4445834b2a3e017419246071","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a9b27322f5114886a70651ad8276dd366232c1a","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0e42b46043a5ea7576f6610937ea9de72291e8b","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1417270a38587e79274e5ef2a02bfd45c6a213b","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2144267fb34f8d7c648b63faf7236f728cfdda54","tid":1340132,"uid":162927,